                        <div>
                            <h3>North Avenue Plant</h3>
                            <p>The North Ave Plant is home to Plenco’s Phenolic Resin, Phenolic Molding Material and Granular 
                                Polyester manufacturing operations, in addition to our Research & Development, Quality Assurance, 
                                Environmental Health & Safety and Maintenance & Engineering Departments. The close relationship 
                                between customers, Sales, Research & Development and Production allows a quick and seamless transition 
                                from custom formulations based on customer’s requirements, lab size batches, scaled all the way to 
                                full production.</p>
                            <p>A source of pride for Plenco is the internal expertise of our Engineering and Maintenance departments 
                                who plan, install and maintain all the process equipment. This intimate knowledge of all our 
                                manufacturing processes allows employee safety and product quality to be designed into every process, 
                                as well as giving Plenco the ability to quickly modify production equipment to meet customer’s needs.</p>
